1.*Odbio* je da učestvuje u raspravi (He refused to take part in the discussion).
2. Ona je *odbila* da vidi goste (She refused to see the guests).
3. On je *odbio* da pomogne (He refused to help).
4. Nešto je *odbilo* da radi (Something refused to work).
5. Oni su *odbili* da se pridruže grupi (They refused to join the group).